    {
      "id": "69cde2ce0000000000c26ead",
      "text": "[[日記]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100621,
      "updated": 1775100621
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde2ce0000000000c26eae",
      "text": " [最適なプログラミング言語]問題、わからん",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100621,
      "updated": 1775100719
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde3300000000000c26ebd",
      "text": " 　Rustいいぞって言われてるけどあんま大規模プロジェクトで採用されてなさそうに見える気もしてた",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100719,
      "updated": 1775100874
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde3550000000000c26ebe",
      "text": " 　[TypeScript 7]では結局[Go言語]だったし",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100756,
      "updated": 1775100778
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde36b0000000000c26ebf",
      "text": " 　　あれはJSからの置き換えの手間が少ないってのが一番の理由だったみたいだけど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100778,
      "updated": 1775100802
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde3900000000000c26ec2",
      "text": " 　　esbuildもGo言語",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100815,
      "updated": 1775100878
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde3cf0000000000c26ec4",
      "text": " 　Rust採用してるやつ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100878,
      "updated": 1775100883
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde3990000000000c26ec3",
      "text": " 　 [Rolldown]はRust",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100824,
      "updated": 1775100865
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde4c90000000000c26ec8",
      "text": " 　  [Vite 8]が採用してるやつ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775101128,
      "updated": 1775101140
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde4140000000000c26ec5",
      "text": " 　 [Oxlint]（[Oxc]ベース）もRust",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100946,
      "updated": 1775100969
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde42b0000000000c26ec6",
      "text": " 　 [Misskey]も部分的にRustを使ってるらしい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100970,
      "updated": 1775100982
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde4470000000000c26ec7",
      "text": " 　 あれ、やっぱ割とあるな",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100997,
      "updated": 1775101004
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde2ce0000000000c26eb7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100621,
      "updated": 1775100621
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde2ce0000000000c26eb8",
      "text": "[[タスク]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100621,
      "updated": 1775100621
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde2ce0000000000c26eb9",
      "text": "\t就活",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100621,
      "updated": 1775100621
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde2ce0000000000c26eba",
      "text": "\t\t✅️[職務経歴書]書く",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1775100621,
      "updated": 1775100629
    },
    {
      "id": "69cde2d80000000000c26ebc",
